Working Features
- Basic game functionality with two different views
- Card placement on the game board
- Card selection
- Turn switching between players
- Display of player hands on both sides
- Color coding (red/blue) for different players
- Score tracking
- Win condition detection
- Card battle/flipping mechanics
- AI player strategies
- Provider's view display and interaction
- Command line arguments still work as before

